01:05:09.073 --> 01:05:11.409
[jazz music playing]

01:05:11.492 --> 01:05:13.286
♪♪

01:05:39.770 --> 01:05:41.564
I ain't interrupting nothing,
am I?

01:05:42.940 --> 01:05:44.650
