01:09:39.551 --> 01:09:41.053
Come here.
Come here.

01:09:41.136 --> 01:09:43.471
- [grunting]
- [screaming]

01:09:46.809 --> 01:09:48.102
No!

01:09:48.185 --> 01:09:49.103
[screaming]

01:09:49.185 --> 01:09:50.645
You goddamn bitch.

